{"tid":1921758,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"求分析，我究竟應唔應該買車，買的話買邊款好？","createTime":"2020-03-12T07:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T14:04:21.000Z","uid":5632,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c170d505ea2753b19bebdb997d326ab1b3b29b26","tid":1921758,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"Hi Chingssssss,<br />\n先少少簡介，我住西貢村屋，自己有架錢7(1244 cc)揸左兩年多。<br />\n因為見三月底到期續牌同買保險，所以諗住換過架或者直情唔揸以後搭的士Uber算。<br />\n通常Weekend先揸，或有時落大雨都會揸車返工。<br />\n初頭有諗過換架CT200H，不過係連登問過幾個本身想換呢款車嘅巴打，結果佢地都係買左其他牌子嘅車, 所以我就打消左呢個念頭。<br />\n本身自己諗住用$15萬左右換過架車，但今日忽然係到諗不過換架Tesla Model 3，因為見屋企有得裝叉電。<br />\n如果係你地，大約$35萬budget，你地會換咩車？後排有時會載老人家，無少朋友。<br />\n我自己其實鐘意BMW新3系 / Benz C Class，不過完全out of budget。<br />\n諗Tesla Model 3係因為一黎有一換一優惠，二黎屋企有得叉，又平過油費。牌費又平D，係保險貴D。<br />\n<br />\n求巴打們 比D指引我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4846d668abd49e919790742f1c25db70d85dc9a8","tid":1921758,"uid":91638,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"你換電車原因如果係為慳油錢就真係唔好諗<br />\n除非你話Weekend我係揸uber或者揸左幾百公里一日<br />\n唔係有排你都慳唔到條數"},{"pid":"8ebd5346f77ea8114934107c1969617980fce432","tid":1921758,"uid":23897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"你已經揀咗model 3"},{"pid":"a9b022affc88cd0808733a5a62800f0ceb0d85f6","tid":1921758,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"AE110"},{"pid":"3916ccf54b1797ec6e30d2455b0b898027054d44","tid":1921758,"uid":233817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9b022affc88cd0808733a5a62800f0ceb0d85f6","tid":1921758,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"AE110"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03